Attention Stackchainers and Stackchain enthusiasts!

The monitoring and replying functionalities for NostrSiggy have been deployed on Nostr! Still in testing phase but working pretty reliably! Have to test a few more use cases with replies, multiple relays, and such.

Siggy is responding on the Damus relay (wss://relay.damus.io) for now. It’s super snappy and responds to any note in under 5 seconds (can possibly even lower that time further). Pretty cool!

It isn’t absorbing any information just yet, just replying to notes.

If you submit a note to the Damus relay with #stackjoin, you should hear from it right away! Let me know if you run into any issues.
